X-Play - February 10th, 2009

Dark Side of the Moon 3D

In this episode of X-Play, Adam and Morgan step into the future as they take a look at new 3D gaming technology from NVIDIA. Then, Kristin Adams delivers Afro Samurai tips in Cheat, go all access with the new Ready 2 Rumble Revolution for the Wii and the multiplatform action game, Dark Void. Plus, go behind the scenes with the Moon team and learn about making a first person shooter for the Nintendo DS, Gaming Update and more!
